To run the tool download the following from the repository, Winobuilder.ps1, policies.json, copykey.ps1, recoverykey.bat and firefox configuration.bat
Setup an account on the windows machine as usual. Make sure your connected to a wireless network
Run the "firefox configuration.bat" file, it will ask you if powershell is allowed to make changes to the machine. say yes
Enter in the pc name into powershell when promted 
walk away for a bit
come back and be amazed! 
